claim.claim-text:
1. A method for managing a plurality of printing devices connected on a network, said method comprising the steps of: 
detecting a printing device connected on the network; 
requesting information from the detected printing device; 
receiving the requested information from the printing device; and 
creating a print queue for the printing device based on the received information.

57. Computer-executable process steps stored on a computer-readable medium, said computer-executable process steps for managing a plurality of printing devices on a network, said computer-executable process steps executable to perform a method comprising the steps of: 
detecting a printing device connected on the network; 
requesting information from the detected printing device; 
receiving the requested information from the printing device; and 
creating a print queue for the printing device based on the received information.

85. A computer-readable medium which stores computer-executable process steps, the computer-executable process steps to manage a plurality of printing devices on a network, said computer-executable process steps comprising process steps executable to perform a method comprising the steps of: 
detecting a printing device connected on the network; 
requesting information from the detected printing device; 
receiving the requested information from the printing device; and 
creating a print queue for the printing device based on the received information.
